gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 107, Nets 86
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Nets, 107-86. Tyrese Maxey (26 points, three rebounds, three assists) and Tobias Harris (21 points, eight rebounds) led Philadelphia as Buddy Hield added 19 points, seven rebounds, and five assists. Cam Thomas led the Nets with 18 points. The 76ers finish 47-35 on the year as the Nets finish 32-50.
